description: TEHRAN - Iran made a winning start to their Group A campaign in the AFC Asian Qualifiers - Road to 26 on Thursday as Amir Ghaleneoi’s side handed Kyrgyzstan a 1-0 defeat at Foolad Shahr Stadium.
title: Iran edge Kyrgyzstan in 2026 FIFA World Cup qualifier

description: PARIS – Ali Pirouj of Iran claimed a silver medal at the men’s javelin throw – F13 of the 2024 Paralympic Games on Thursday.
title: Javelin thrower Pirouj claims silver at 2024 Paralympic Games

description: PARIS – Iranian Para athlete Aliasghar Javanmardi of Iran won a bronze medal in the 2024 Paralympic Games on Thursday.
title: 2024 Paralympics: Iran’s Javanmardi wins bronze in shot put

description: PARIS – Iranian judo athlete Meysam Banitaba won a silver medal in the 2024 Paralympic Games on Thursday.
title: Banitaba collects silver at 2024 Paralympics judo

description: TEHRAN - Iran’s para powerlifter Mohsen Bakhtiar won a bronze medal in the 2024 Paralympic Games on Thursday.
title: Bakhtiar takes bronze at powerlifting: 2024 Paralympic Games

description: TEHRAN - Iran’s Foreign Minister Abbas Araqchi has said any threat to the territorial integrity of Iran’s neighbors or redrawing land borders whether in the North, South, East and West is “quite unacceptable” and considered a “red line” by the Islamic Republic.
title: Iran FM: Threats to neighbors’ territorial integrity or redrawing borders is Tehran's ‘red line’

description: PARIS – Iranian discus thrower Hassan Bajoulvand sized a silver medal in the 2024 Paralympic Games on Thursday.
title: Discus thrower Bajoulvand takes silver: 2024 Paralympics

description: PARIS – Iran men’s sitting volleyball team defeated Egypt 3-1 (25-14, 25-15, 20-25, 25-8) in the 2024 Paralympic Games semifinals on Thursday.
title: Iran sitting volleyball one step away from eighth gold at Paralympics

description: Kazem Jalali, Iranian Ambassador to Russia, held a meeting with Adviser to the Russian President Igor Levitin and Chairman of the Russian Iranian Business Council at the Russian Chamber of Commerce and Industry, Leonid Lozhechko. This was reported by the Russian Iranian Business Cooperation Council at the Russian Chamber of Commerce and Industry.
title: Iran's ambassador to Russia meets with Russian presidential adviser
